== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|713 AD|ja|713rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|May 30|ja|5月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|Emperor Genmei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ordered the compilation of the {{ill|Fudoki|ja|風土記|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in various provinces. * {{ill|Yōrō|ja|養老|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|718 AD|ja|718th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The four countries of {{ill|Noto Province|ja|能登国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Ishikuni Province|ja|石城国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , and {{ill|Ishikose Province|ja|石背国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} were established. * {{ill|Kenryaku|ja|建暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1213 AD|ja|1213rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|May 23|ja|5月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|ja|和田義盛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} attacked the {{ill|Kamakura Shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in order to defeat {{ill|Hojo Yoshitoki|ja|北条義時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ; the following day, at {{ill|Yuigahama|ja|由比ヶ浜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , his entire clan was annihilated.
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1599 AD|ja|1599th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Konoe Nobuhira|ja|近衛信尋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a court noble (died {{ill|1649 AD|ja|1649th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|756 AD|ja|756th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 45th Emperor (born {{ill|701 AD|ja|701st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|995 AD|ja|995th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 2|ja|6月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|ja|藤原道綱母|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , author of the {{ill|Chōryō Nikki|ja|蜻蛉日記|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born circa {{ill|936 AD|ja|936th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ?). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1583 AD|ja|1583rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Oda Nobutaka|ja|織田信孝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander and the third son of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1558 AD|ja|1558th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
