{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|713 AD|ja|713rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|May 30|ja|5月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|Emperor Genmei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ordered the compilation of the {{ill|Fudoki|ja|風土記|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in various provinces. * {{ill|Yōrō|ja|養老|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|718 AD|ja|718th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The four countries of {{ill|Noto Province|ja|能登国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Ishikuni Province|ja|石城国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , and {{ill|Ishikose Province|ja|石背国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} were established. * {{ill|Kenryaku|ja|建暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1213 AD|ja|1213rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|May 23|ja|5月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|ja|和田義盛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} attacked the {{ill|Kamakura Shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in order to defeat {{ill|Hojo Yoshitoki|ja|北条義時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ; the following day, at {{ill|Yuigahama|ja|由比ヶ浜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , his entire clan was annihilated.
