{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月初二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 2일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=}} 6th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|713 AD|ja|713rd year|qq=}} {{ill|May 30|ja|5月30日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|Emperor Genmei|qq=}} ordered the compilation of the {{ill|Fudoki|ja|風土記|qq=}} in various provinces. * {{ill|Yōrō|ja|養老|qq=}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|718 AD|ja|718th year|qq=}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=}} ) – The four countries of {{ill|Noto Province|ja|能登国|qq=}} , {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|qq=}} , {{ill|Ishikuni Province|ja|石城国|qq=}} , and {{ill|Ishikose Province|ja|石背国|qq=}} were established. * {{ill|Kenryaku|ja|建暦|qq=}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1213 AD|ja|1213rd year|qq=}} {{ill|May 23|ja|5月23日|qq=}} ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|qq=}} , {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|ja|和田義盛|qq=}} attacked the {{ill|Kamakura Shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=}} in order to defeat {{ill|Hojo Yoshitoki|ja|北条義時|qq=}} ; the following day, at {{ill|Yuigahama|ja|由比ヶ浜|qq=}} , his entire clan was annihilated.
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1599 AD|ja|1599th year|qq=}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Konoe Nobuhira|ja|近衛信尋|qq=}} , a court noble (died {{ill|1649 AD|ja|1649th year|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|qq=}} 8 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|756 AD|ja|756th year|qq=}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|qq=}} , the 45th Emperor (born {{ill|701 AD|ja|701st year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|995 AD|ja|995th year|qq=}} {{ill|June 2|ja|6月2日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|ja|藤原道綱母|qq=}} , author of the {{ill|Chōryō Nikki|ja|蜻蛉日記|qq=}} (born circa {{ill|936 AD|ja|936th year|qq=}} ?). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 11th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1583 AD|ja|1583rd year|qq=}} {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Oda Nobutaka|ja|織田信孝|qq=}} , a military commander and the third son of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=}} (born {{ill|1558 AD|ja|1558th year|qq=}} ).
