== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|qq=|12=draft}} 8 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|756 AD|ja|756th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 45th Emperor (born {{ill|701 AD|ja|701st year|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|qq=|12=draft}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|995 AD|ja|995th year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 2|ja|6月2日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|ja|藤原道綱母|qq=|12=draft}} , author of the {{ill|Chōryō Nikki|ja|蜻蛉日記|qq=|12=draft}} (born circa {{ill|936 AD|ja|936th year|qq=|12=draft}} ?). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}} 11th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1583 AD|ja|1583rd year|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Oda Nobutaka|ja|織田信孝|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander and the third son of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1558 AD|ja|1558th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
