== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=|qq=draft}} 6th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|713 AD|ja|713rd year|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|May 30|ja|5月30日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|Emperor Genmei|qq=|qq=draft}} ordered the compilation of the {{ill|Fudoki|ja|風土記|qq=|qq=draft}} in various provinces. * {{ill|Yōrō|ja|養老|qq=|qq=draft}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|718 AD|ja|718th year|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – The four countries of {{ill|Noto Province|ja|能登国|qq=|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|qq=|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Ishikuni Province|ja|石城国|qq=|qq=draft}} , and {{ill|Ishikose Province|ja|石背国|qq=|qq=draft}} were established. * {{ill|Kenryaku|ja|建暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1213 AD|ja|1213rd year|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|May 23|ja|5月23日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|qq=|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|ja|和田義盛|qq=|qq=draft}} attacked the {{ill|Kamakura Shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|qq=draft}} in order to defeat {{ill|Hojo Yoshitoki|ja|北条義時|qq=|qq=draft}} ; the following day, at {{ill|Yuigahama|ja|由比ヶ浜|qq=|qq=draft}} , his entire clan was annihilated.
