endar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1583 AD|ja|1583rd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1583 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Oda Nobutaka|ja|織田信孝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobutaka|qq=}} , a military commander and the third son of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobunaga|qq=}} (born {{ill|1558 AD|ja|1558th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1558 AD|qq=}} ).
