d Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1213 AD|ja|1213rd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1213 AD|qq=}} {{ill|May 23|ja|5月23日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 23|qq=}} ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wada War|qq=}} , {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|ja|和田義盛|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wada Yoshimori|qq=}} attacked the {{ill|Kamakura Shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamakura Shogunate|qq=}} in order to defeat {{ill|Hojo Yoshitoki|ja|北条義時|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hojo Yoshitoki|qq=}} ; the following day, at {{ill|Yuigahama|ja|由比ヶ浜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuigahama|qq=}} , his entire clan was annihilated.
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1599 AD|ja|1599th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1599 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 24|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Konoe Nobuhira|ja|近衛信尋|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konoe Nobuhira|qq=}} , a court noble (died {{ill|1649 AD|ja|1649th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1649 AD|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennpyō Shōhō|qq=}} 8 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|756 AD|ja|756th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/756 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 4|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Shōmu|qq=}} , the 45th Emperor (born {{ill|701 AD|ja|701st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/701 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōtoku|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|995 AD|ja|995th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/995 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 2|ja|6月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 2|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|ja|藤原道綱母|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|qq=}} , author of the {{ill|Chōryō Nikki|ja|蜻蛉日記|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōryō Nikki|qq=}} (born circa {{ill|936 AD|ja|936th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/936 AD|qq=}} ?). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 11th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1583 AD|ja|1583rd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1583 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Oda Nobutaka|ja|織田信孝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobutaka|qq=}} , a military commander and the third son of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobunaga|qq=}} (born {{ill|1558 AD|ja|1558th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1558 AD|qq=}} ).
