== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennpyō Shōhō|qq=}} 8 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|756 AD|ja|756年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/756 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 4|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Shōmu|qq=}} , the 45th Emperor (born {{ill|701 AD|ja|701st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/701 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōtoku|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|995 AD|ja|995年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/995 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 2|ja|6月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 2|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|ja|藤原道綱母|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|qq=}} , author of the {{ill|Chōryō Nikki|ja|蜻蛉日記|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōryō Nikki|qq=}} (born circa {{ill|936 AD|ja|936年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/936 AD|qq=}} ?). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 11th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian 