{{Not to be confused with|May 2|qq=May 2}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月初二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 2일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}} .
== Events == * [[:en:Wadō (era)|Wadō]] 6th Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:713|713 AD]] [[:en:May 30|May 30]] ) – {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|Emperor Genmei|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Genmei|qq=}} ordered the compilation of the [[:en:Fudoki|Fudoki]] in various provinces. * [[:en:Yōrō|Yōrō]] 2nd Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:718|718 AD]] [[:en:June 4|June 4]] ) – The four countries of [[:en:Noto Province|Noto Province]] , [[:en:Awa Province (Chiba)|Awa Province]] , [[:en:Iwaki Province (718)|Ishikuni Province]] , and [[:en:Iwase Province|Ishikose Province]] were established. * [[:en:Kenryaku|Kenryaku]] 3rd Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1213|1213 AD]] [[:en:May 23|May 23]] ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wada War|qq=}} , [[:en:Wada Yoshimori|Wada Yoshimori]] attacked the [[:en:Kamakura shogunate|Kamakura Shogunate]] in order to defeat [[:en:Hōjō Yoshitoki|Hojo Yoshitoki]] ; the following day, at [[:en:Yuigahama|Yuigahama]] , his entire clan was annihilated.
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 4th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1599|1599 AD]] [[:en:June 24|June 24]] ) – [[:en:Konoe Nobuhiro|Konoe Nobuhira]] , a court noble (died [[:en:1649|1649 AD]] ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennpyō Shōhō|qq=}} 8 ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:756|756 AD]] [[:en:June 4|June 4]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Shōmu|Emperor Shōmu]] , the 45th Emperor (born [[:en:701|701 AD]] ). * [[:en:Chōtoku|Chōtoku]] 1st Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:995|995 AD]] [[:en:June 2|June 2]] ) – [[:en:Michitsuna's mother|Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto]] , author of the [[:en:Kagerō Nikki|Chōryō Nikki]] (born circa [[:en:936|936 AD]] ?). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 11th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1583|1583 AD]] [[:en:June 21|June 21]] ) – [[:en:Oda Nobutaka|Oda Nobutaka]] , a military commander and the third son of [[:en:Oda Nobunaga|Oda Nobunaga]] (born [[:en:1558|1558 AD]] ).
