{{Lunisolar May|qq=}} 
'''May 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}  the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|1=Shakkō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11635368}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Wadō (era)|en|Wadō (era)|qid=Q1373026|lt=Wadō|1=Wadō (era)}}  6th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|713|en|713|qid=Q23523|lt=713 AD|1=713}}  {{ill|May 30|en|May 30|qid=Q2590|lt=May 30|1=May 30}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|Emperor Genmei|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Genmei|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}  ordered the compilation of the {{ill|Fudoki|en|Fudoki|qid=Q1194534|lt=Fudoki|1=Fudoki}}  in various provinces.
* {{ill|Yōrō|en|Yōrō|qid=Q1373061|lt=Yōrō|1=Yōrō}}  2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|718|en|718|qid=Q23534|lt=718 AD|1=718}}  {{ill|June 4|en|June 4|qid=Q2627|lt=June 4|1=June 4}} ) – The four countries of {{ill|Noto Province|en|Noto Province|qid=Q1047671|lt=Noto Province|1=Noto Province}} , {{ill|Awa Province (Chiba)|en|Awa Province (Chiba)|qid=Q1053044|lt=Awa Province|1=Awa Province (Chiba)}} , {{ill|Iwaki Province (718)|en|Iwaki Province (718)|qid=Q1192809|lt=Ishikuni Province|1=Iwaki Province (718)}} , and {{ill|Iwase Province|en|Iwase Province|qid=Q1166897|lt=Ishikose Province|1=Iwase Province}}  were established.
* {{ill|Kenryaku|en|Kenryaku|qid=Q1194260|lt=Kenryaku|1=Kenryaku}}  3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|1213|en|1213|qid=Q5261|lt=1213 AD|1=1213}}  {{ill|May 23|en|May 23|qid=Q2583|lt=May 23|1=May 23}} ) – In the {{ill|Wada War|ja|和田合戦|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wada War|1=Wada Rebellion|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11417941}} , {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|en|Wada Yoshimori|qid=Q3564968|lt=Wada Yoshimori|1=Wada Yoshimori}}  attacked the {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|en|Kamakura shogunate|qid=Q736839|lt=Kamakura Shogunate|1=Kamakura shogunate}}  in order to defeat {{ill|Hōjō Yoshitoki|en|Hōjō Yoshitoki|qid=Q1028811|lt=Hojo Yoshitoki|1=Hōjō Yoshitoki}} ; the following day, at {{ill|Yuigahama|en|Yuigahama|qid=Q8060490|lt=Yuigahama|1=Yuigahama}} , his entire clan was annihilated.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Keichō|en|Keichō|qid=Q1328185|lt=Keichō|1=Keichō}}  4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1599|en|1599|qid=Q6803|lt=1599 AD|1=1599}}  {{ill|June 24|en|June 24|qid=Q2665|lt=June 24|1=June 24}} ) – {{ill|Konoe Nobuhiro|en|Konoe Nobuhiro|qid=Q923621|lt=Konoe Nobuhira|1=Konoe Nobuhiro}} , a court noble (died {{ill|1649|en|1649|qid=Q6945|lt=1649 AD|1=1649}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Tennpyō Shōhō|ja|Tenpyō勝宝|1=Tenpyō-shōhō|2=ja|3=天平勝宝|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennpyō Shōhō|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1373169}}  8 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|756|en|756|qid=Q31121|lt=756 AD|1=756}}  {{ill|June 4|en|June 4|qid=Q2627|lt=June 4|1=June 4}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Shōmu|en|Emperor Shōmu|qid=Q349263|lt=Emperor Shōmu|1=Emperor Shōmu}} , the 45th Emperor (born {{ill|701|en|701|qid=Q23496|lt=701 AD|1=701}} ).
* {{ill|Chōtoku|en|Chōtoku|qid=Q1327213|lt=Chōtoku|1=Chōtoku}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|995|en|995|qid=Q23794|lt=995 AD|1=995}}  {{ill|June 2|en|June 2|qid=Q2624|lt=June 2|1=June 2}} ) – {{ill|Michitsuna's mother|en|Michitsuna's mother|qid=Q439829|lt=Fujiwara no Michitsunemoto|1=Michitsuna's mother}} , author of the {{ill|Kagerō Nikki|en|Kagerō Nikki|qid=Q3005729|lt=Chōryō Nikki|1=Kagerō Nikki}}  (born circa {{ill|936|en|936|qid=Q23584|lt=936 AD|1=936}} ?).
* {{ill|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|en|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qid=Q1145058|lt=Tenshō Era|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)}}  11th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1583|en|1583|qid=Q6726|lt=1583 AD|1=1583}}  {{ill|June 21|en|June 21|qid=Q2671|lt=June 21|1=June 21}} ) – {{ill|Oda Nobutaka|en|Oda Nobutaka|qid=Q2614349|lt=Oda Nobutaka|1=Oda Nobutaka}} , a military commander and the third son of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|en|Oda Nobunaga|qid=Q171411|lt=Oda Nobunaga|1=Oda Nobunaga}}  (born {{ill|1558|en|1558|qid=Q6601|lt=1558 AD|1=1558}} ).

